---
import ContentLayout from "../layouts/ContentLayout.astro";
---

<ContentLayout
    title="Academic Classroom Grants"
    description="Supporting teachers with funding for innovative classroom projects and educational materials that enhance student learning."
    showBreadcrumbs={true}
    breadcrumbs={[
        { name: "Foundation Initiatives", href: "/foundation-initiatives" },
        { name: "Academic Classroom Grants", href: "/academic-class-grants" }
    ]}
>
    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Empowering Educators, Enriching Learning</h2>
        <p>
            Green Schools Foundation's Academic Classroom Grants program provides direct funding to teachers and staff for innovative educational projects, classroom materials, and learning experiences that go beyond the traditional curriculum.
        </p>
        <p>
            Since our founding, we have awarded thousands of dollars in classroom grants, supporting everything from STEM equipment and literacy programs to arts supplies and technology initiatives that enhance student engagement and achievement.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-4">2024-2025 Grant Applications</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Application Period</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Opens:</strong> September 1st</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6 2a1 1 0 00-1 1v1H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-1V3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1H7V3a1 1 0 00-1-1zm0 5a1 1 0 000 2h8a1 1 0 100-2H6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Deadline:</strong> December 15th</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Awards Announced:</strong> February</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Grant Information</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2V6h10a2 2 0 00-2-2H4zm2 6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H8a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4zm6 4a2 2 0 100-4 2 2 0 000 4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Award Range:</strong> $100 - $2,000</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Eligible:</strong> All Green Local Schools staff</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span><strong>Multiple applications</strong> encouraged</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>What We Fund</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2.22l.123.489.804.804A1 1 0 0113 18H7a1 1 0 01-.707-1.707l.804-.804L7.22 15H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zm5.771 7H5V5h10v7H8.771z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Technology & Equipment</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-none pl-0 [&>li]:mb-1">
                            <li>Educational software and apps</li>
                            <li>STEM equipment and robotics kits</li>
                            <li>Interactive whiteboards and projectors</li>
                            <li>Tablets and computer accessories</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Curriculum Materials</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-none pl-0 [&>li]:mb-1">
                            <li>Books and reading materials</li>
                            <li>Educational games and manipulatives</li>
                            <li>Science lab supplies</li>
                            <li>Art and craft materials</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Field Trip Experiences</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-none pl-0 [&>li]:mb-1">
                            <li>Transportation costs</li>
                            <li>Admission fees</li>
                            <li>Educational program costs</li>
                            <li>Overnight trip expenses</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Special Programs</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-none pl-0 [&>li]:mb-1">
                            <li>Guest speaker fees</li>
                            <li>Workshop materials</li>
                            <li>Competition entry fees</li>
                            <li>Enrichment activities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.395 2.553a1 1 0 00-1.45-.385c-.345.23-.614.558-.822.88-.214.33-.403.713-.57 1.116-.334.804-.614 1.768-.84 2.734a31.365 31.365 0 00-.613 3.58 2.64 2.64 0 01-.945-1.067c-.328-.68-.398-1.534-.398-2.654A1 1 0 005.05 6.05 6.981 6.981 0 003 11a7 7 0 1011.95-4.95c-.592-.591-.98-.985-1.348-1.467-.363-.476-.724-1.063-1.207-2.03zM12.12 15.12A3 3 0 017 13s.879.5 2.5.5c0-1 .5-4 1.25-4.5.5 1 .786 1.293 1.371 1.879A2.99 2.99 0 0113 13a2.99 2.99 0 01-.879 2.121z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Creative Projects</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-none pl-0 [&>li]:mb-1">
                            <li>Music instruments and equipment</li>
                            <li>Drama and theater supplies</li>
                            <li>Art exhibition materials</li>
                            <li>Creative writing resources</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Classroom Environment</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 list-none pl-0 [&>li]:mb-1">
                            <li>Flexible seating options</li>
                            <li>Storage and organization systems</li>
                            <li>Classroom decorations</li>
                            <li>Learning station materials</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>How to Apply</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 mt-1">
                    1
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Develop Your Project</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Identify a specific educational need or opportunity in your classroom or school. Consider how your project will directly benefit student learning and engagement.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 mt-1">
                    2
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Complete the Application</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Download and complete the grant application form. Include detailed information about your project, budget, timeline, and expected outcomes.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 mt-1">
                    3
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Submit Your Application</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Submit your completed application by the December 15th deadline. Late applications will not be considered.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 mt-1">
                    4
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Review & Award Process</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Applications are reviewed by our board members and awards are announced in February. Recipients will be recognized at our Celebration of Education event.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section">
        <h2>Success Stories</h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
            Our classroom grants have supported countless innovative projects that have enhanced learning experiences for Green Local Schools students. Here are just a few examples of recently funded projects:
        </p>

        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2.22l.123.489.804.804A1 1 0 0113 18H7a1 1 0 01-.707-1.707l.804-.804L7.22 15H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5zm5.771 7H5V5h10v7H8.771z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">STEM Learning Stations</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                    A 4th grade teacher received $1,500 to create interactive STEM learning stations, including coding robots and engineering challenge kits that increased student engagement by 40%.
                </p>
                <div class="text-primary-600 text-sm font-medium">Award: $1,500</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M9 4.804A7.968 7.968 0 005.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804v10A7.969 7.969 0 015.5 14c1.669 0 3.218.51 4.5 1.385A7.962 7.962 0 0114.5 14c1.255 0 2.443.29 3.5.804v-10A7.968 7.968 0 0014.5 4c-1.255 0-2.443.29-3.5.804V12a1 1 0 11-2 0V4.804z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Classroom Library Expansion</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                    High school English teachers collaborated to expand their classroom libraries with diverse, contemporary literature, resulting in a 25% increase in independent reading.
                </p>
                <div class="text-accent-600 text-sm font-medium">Award: $800</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.395 2.553a1 1 0 00-1.45-.385c-.345.23-.614.558-.822.88-.214.33-.403.713-.57 1.116-.334.804-.614 1.768-.84 2.734a31.365 31.365 0 00-.613 3.58 2.64 2.64 0 01-.945-1.067c-.328-.68-.398-1.534-.398-2.654A1 1 0 005.05 6.05 6.981 6.981 0 003 11a7 7 0 1011.95-4.95c-.592-.591-.98-.985-1.348-1.467-.363-.476-.724-1.063-1.207-2.03zM12.12 15.12A3 3 0 017 13s.879.5 2.5.5c0-1 .5-4 1.25-4.5.5 1 .786 1.293 1.371 1.879A2.99 2.99 0 0113 13a2.99 2.99 0 01-.879 2.121z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Science Lab Equipment</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                    Middle school science teachers received funding for microscopes and lab equipment, enabling hands-on experiments that improved test scores by 15%.
                </p>
                <div class="text-secondary-600 text-sm font-medium">Award: $2,000</div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Field Trip Adventures</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">
                    Elementary classes visited the Cleveland Museum of Natural History, bringing their dinosaur unit to life and inspiring several students to pursue paleontology interests.
                </p>
                <div class="text-green-600 text-sm font-medium">Award: $600</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-section text-center">
        <h2>Ready to Apply?</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
            Have an innovative idea that could enhance learning in your classroom? We'd love to help make it happen.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:greenschoolsfoundation@gmail.com?subject=Classroom Grant Application" class="button-primary mr-4">
            Request Application
        </a>
        <a href="/celebration-of-education" class="button-secondary">
            See Past Recipients
        </a>
    </div>
</ContentLayout>
